OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPolice Scotland postpones  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fclean-shaven policy        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Police Scotland has postponed a new    
OL,6, clean-shaven policy after taking health
OL,7, and safety advice and listening to     
OL,8, officers, the force has said.          
OL,10,FThe policy, already delayed from May,  
OL,11,Fwould need many frontline officers and 
OL,12,Fstaff to remove beards and moustaches. 
OL,14,FThe Scottish Police Federation (SPF),  
OL,15,Fthe LGBTI Police Association and others
OL,16,Fcriticised the plans and four officers 
OL,17,Ftook legal action.                     
OL,19,FPolice Scotland said the policy would  
OL,20,Fbe reviewed again in 12 months.        
